Celebrities came through to support Calif Record's Clemmo at the funeral fundraiser for his mother at All Saints Cathedral on Tuesday.In attendance were Johnstone Sakaja, Nonini, Refigah, Ala C, Jua Cali, Jimwatt, Kajairo, Mdomo Baggy, Nameless, Producer Musyoka, among others.Sakaja said Clemmo was a longtime pal of his and "when I got the news, I was shocked. I had to come and support my friend."Mary Akinyi Rapudo died of a heart attack late March after falling sick for a few days. The body left Chiromo yesterday for Shauri Moyo then Calif. It will be transported to Gem and thereafter for the burial on Saturday.